    "name": "星绘友晴天 Demo",
    "steam_appid": 4313570,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/8c5c0493c398f3b65c7d6a2d070ff3bb.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1080 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🎉 感谢每一位点下&quot;开始游戏&quot;的你</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各位星星探险家们，你们好！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢大家在本次Steam新品节中，选择了我们的游戏。谢谢你们，让立方星在这个冬天亮了起来✨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>📮 你的每一条反馈，我们都会认真听</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开发组非常期待听到大家的真实感受——夸夸也好，吐槽也好，“这里是不是有bug”也好，每一条声音对我们来说都是珍贵的礼物。我们不是说说而已，是真的会听，真的会改。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入我们的官方QQ交流群，来和开发组零距离唠嗑吧～</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>QQ群号：1050873718</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里没有距离感，只有一群想把游戏变得更好的同行者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔔 关于本次测试的重要说明</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本次Demo为 Steam新品节专享删档测试，活动结束后Demo将下架，存档也会被星星带走～请大家知悉✨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们清楚地知道，当前的Demo还不够完美，有些地方可能还略显粗糙——但你们发现的每一处不足，都已经被我们悄悄记在小本本上了。接下来的日子，我们会带着大家的反馈，一点一点把它打磨成我们共同期待的样子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是终点，而是起点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >再次感谢每一位愿意在这个阶段就陪伴我们的玩家，我们不会辜负这份信任。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >下次见面的时候，希望能给大家带来更多惊喜🌟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>——星绘友晴天开发组 全体成员</i><br>————————————————————————————————————————————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《星绘友晴天》是一款人人都能玩的养成系社交游戏，它集合了充满治愈的“生活模拟”和充满创意的“欢乐派对”两种游戏类型，并致力于让任何一类玩家都能找到属于自己的游玩体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/f7e21fbe324f70375d973071b4c4542a.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1560 height=172 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为宇宙英雄候选人的重要任务，你需要以自己的星球为基地，深入探索光明宇宙与黑暗宇宙的边缘的群星地带。这需要你制造更强大的火箭，和朋友们一起组成英雄小队，持续去追踪隐藏在群星深处的秘密和故事，搜集全宇宙的宝藏，才能最终打败黑暗力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/f5ad339a8f3636417798e6de3482822b.poster.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/f5ad339a8f3636417798e6de3482822b.webm?t=1772095202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/d7f97ca3d0bbb3926efcda510e4e43e5.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1560 height=173 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >外星生活不易，但你的万能机器人PADI将来帮助你。它能变成滑板、汽车、收割机、船舶、飞行器、钓竿、食物摊位、照相机、扫描仪甚至是心灵探测器……你需要不断解锁PADI的能力，PADI的扫描仪能够扫描物件并获得图纸，帮助你不断增加见闻，每玩一个小游戏、解锁一个成就或获得一个新物品，都会丰富你的见闻。每十个新的见闻便能填满一本见闻书。你会跟PADI一起搜集万物，不断解锁新能力，成为宇宙英雄的候选人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/b67b14c53b5a5d908010f6bdcfa5994e.poster.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/b67b14c53b5a5d908010f6bdcfa5994e.webm?t=1772095202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/752474c28c0bc17536557bead10c693b.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1560 height=173 /></span>你的星球将逐步接收全宇宙的不同背景和充满独特故事的居民们搬入，超过40名。作为社区的领袖，你为他们建设好住宅，常和他们互动聊天，他们就会逐步和你成最好的伙伴。你会帮他们建设各种游乐和体育设施，让星球的居民更幸福的生活。不仅如此，你现在还可以与好友一起共建星球，增强互动与合作的乐趣。每颗星球最多支持4人共建，这意味着你可以与好友们共同创造美好的回忆，携手打造一个独一无二的奇妙星球，一起探索星球地心和漫天繁星的秘密！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/12e24a77c3c4592ffab55586f29a6d3b.poster.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/12e24a77c3c4592ffab55586f29a6d3b.webm?t=1772095202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/9307186e881722d140ee13101edde9dd.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1560 height=173 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宇宙中每个玩家的初始星球都不一样，但你可以通过努力，美化环境，开垦土地，种植各种农作物；在野外水域垂钓鱼类甚至经营鱼类养殖场，捕捉各种神奇昆虫；挖掘矿石和遗迹，捐赠给博物馆或制作道具；开设各类商店、建设游乐园、商店街、体育场…...接待来自全宇宙游客，带领居民们一起赚全宇宙游客的钱！在立方星，你可以通过经营致富，每次完成星球公司的股份回购，熊老大都会给你更大的房子作为奖励。随着星球的发展，会有更多游客来旅游消费。别忘记，他们拥有各自不同的日程，了解他们的故事，满足他们的心愿、收获他们的微笑，让星球越来越好。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/8ea3e0d52a08201d8982921a63d13be2.poster.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/8ea3e0d52a08201d8982921a63d13be2.webm?t=1772095202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/8f835c84f8b0f26451a6d6d6f2f16842.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1560 height=173 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宇宙中有许多和你一样的英雄候选人，宇宙联合国每天会给全宇宙发布一份活动日程，将有超过120个多人派对迷你游戏按照每20分钟一次发布出来。只要你有空闲就可以个人或组队报名参加。星际派对会把32位英雄组合起来一起参加4个随机迷你游戏，欢乐派对会以三轮淘汰制玩一个相同的迷你游戏，英雄派对将决出宇宙电竞巡回赛的外卡门票。无论是队友还是对手，一起party过的朋友们都将出现在你的朋友圈中！如果你想加速你的星球发展进度，参加派对和电竞活动准没错，会有丰厚的奖励！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/371f06642539293c7b19a3f328000df1.poster.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/371f06642539293c7b19a3f328000df1.webm?t=1772095202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/a0d824b4e0b9f9832c0a216a0a01c278.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1560 height=173 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供简单但强大的游戏设计编辑器，你可以创建自己的迷你游戏，从竞速、跳跃、解谜，到2D、合作、竞技。你不仅可以邀请您游戏中的朋友们一起体验，还能把它在线发布出来，让全世界的玩家都来体验。甚至你举办的电竞比赛，也可以让全世界的高手们来报名挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/a6e1e8b02e53cb14879a4d990066ffa0.poster.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/a6e1e8b02e53cb14879a4d990066ffa0.webm?t=1772095202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/4f097bd7f9e402a27a8b2c0365abbe87.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1560 height=173 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过10万根毛发的高质量渲染角色，让你任性捏脸。你能搜集来自宇宙各地的帽子、衣服、眼镜、鞋子来穿搭出你的风格，用各式各样的家具来布置房间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/63591fd62bca6b4862219f2e968b2f14.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/46c13655122d6b36902d4716f15df2b2.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1560 height=173 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以与好友联机，一同享受这段快乐的宇宙时光。白天种种地，晚上开Party！一切尽在《星绘友晴天》！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313570/extras/60aaa2b6ebc34968cd16fb9372447f45.avif?t=1772095202\" width=1560 height=876 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
